### Pomodoro Web Page
- **Objective:** Develop a web page to explain the Pomodoro technique using HTML and CSS.
- **Method:** Created a webpage with semantic HTML elements, styling it using CSS, and included visual enhancements with images and styled text.
- **Outcome:** Developed an informative and aesthetically pleasing web page to explain the Pomodoro technique.

